      <Math mode="display" tex="\begin{array}[]{lll}[{J}_{ab},{J}_{ac}]={J}_{bc}&amp;\qquad[{J}_{ab},{J}_{bc}]=-{J%&#10;}_{ac}&amp;\qquad[{J}_{ac},{J}_{bc}]={J}_{ab}\\&#10;{}[{M}_{ab},{M}_{ac}]={J}_{bc}&amp;\qquad[{M}_{ab},{M}_{bc}]={J}_{ac}&amp;\qquad[{M}_{%&#10;ac},{M}_{bc}]={J}_{ab}\\&#10;{}[{J}_{ab},{M}_{ac}]={M}_{bc}&amp;\qquad[{J}_{ab},{M}_{bc}]=-{M}_{ac}&amp;\qquad[{J}_%&#10;{ac},{M}_{bc}]=-{M}_{ab}\\&#10;{}[{M}_{ab},{J}_{ac}]=-{M}_{bc}&amp;\qquad[{M}_{ab},{J}_{bc}]=-{M}_{ac}&amp;\qquad[{M}%&#10;_{ac},{J}_{bc}]={M}_{ab}\\&#10;{}[{J}_{ab},{J}_{de}]=0&amp;\qquad[{M}_{ab},{M}_{de}]=0&amp;\qquad[{J}_{ab},{M}_{de}]=%&#10;0\\&#10;\omit\span\omit\span\omit[{J}_{ab},{B}_{l}]=(\delta_{a,l-1}-\delta_{b,l-1}+%&#10;\delta_{bl}-\delta_{al}){M}_{ab}\\&#10;\omit\span\omit\span\omit[{M}_{ab},{B}_{l}]=-(\delta_{a,l-1}-\delta_{b,l-1}+%&#10;\delta_{bl}-\delta_{al}){J}_{ab}\end{array}" text="Array[[closed-interval@(J _ (a * b), J _ (a * c)) = J _ (b * c), closed-interval@(J _ (a * b), J _ (b * c)) = - J _ (a * c), closed-interval@(J _ (a * c), J _ (b * c)) = J _ (a * b)], [closed-interval@(M _ (a * b), M _ (a * c)) = J _ (b * c), closed-interval@(M _ (a * b), M _ (b * c)) = J _ (a * c), closed-interval@(M _ (a * c), M _ (b * c)) = J _ (a * b)], [closed-interval@(J _ (a * b), M _ (a * c)) = M _ (b * c), closed-interval@(J _ (a * b), M _ (b * c)) = - M _ (a * c), closed-interval@(J _ (a * c), M _ (b * c)) = - M _ (a * b)], [closed-interval@(M _ (a * b), J _ (a * c)) = - M _ (b * c), closed-interval@(M _ (a * b), J _ (b * c)) = - M _ (a * c), closed-interval@(M _ (a * c), J _ (b * c)) = M _ (a * b)], [closed-interval@(J _ (a * b), J _ (d * e)) = 0, closed-interval@(M _ (a * b), M _ (d * e)) = 0, closed-interval@(J _ (a * b), M _ (d * e)) = 0], [closed-interval@(J _ (a * b), B _ l) = (((delta _ (list@(a, l - 1)) - delta _ (list@(b, l - 1))) + delta _ (b * l)) - delta _ (a * l)) * M _ (a * b)], [closed-interval@(M _ (a * b), B _ l) = - (((delta _ (list@(a, l - 1)) - delta _ (list@(b, l - 1))) + delta _ (b * l)) - delta _ (a * l)) * J _ (a * b)]]" xml:id="S0.E2.m1">

      <Math mode="display" tex="\begin{array}[]{lll}[{J}_{ab},{J}_{ac}]={\omega}_{ab}{J}_{bc}&amp;\qquad[{J}_{ab},%&#10;{J}_{bc}]=-{J}_{ac}&amp;\qquad[{J}_{ac},{J}_{bc}]={\omega}_{bc}{J}_{ab}\\&#10;{}[{M}_{ab},{M}_{ac}]={\omega}_{ab}{J}_{bc}&amp;\qquad[{M}_{ab},{M}_{bc}]={J}_{ac}%&#10;&amp;\qquad[{M}_{ac},{M}_{bc}]={\omega}_{bc}{J}_{ab}\\&#10;{}[{J}_{ab},{M}_{ac}]={\omega}_{ab}{M}_{bc}&amp;\qquad[{J}_{ab},{M}_{bc}]=-{M}_{ac%&#10;}&amp;\qquad[{J}_{ac},{M}_{bc}]=-{\omega}_{bc}{M}_{ab}\\&#10;{}[{M}_{ab},{J}_{ac}]=-{\omega}_{ab}{M}_{bc}&amp;\qquad[{M}_{ab},{J}_{bc}]=-{M}_{%&#10;ac}&amp;\qquad[{M}_{ac},{J}_{bc}]={\omega}_{bc}{M}_{ab}\\&#10;{}[{J}_{ab},{J}_{de}]=0&amp;\qquad[{M}_{ab},{M}_{de}]=0&amp;\qquad[{J}_{ab},{M}_{de}]=%&#10;0\\&#10;\omit\span\omit\span\omit[{J}_{ab},{B}_{l}]=(\delta_{a,l-1}-\delta_{b,l-1}+%&#10;\delta_{bl}-\delta_{al}){M}_{ab}\\&#10;\omit\span\omit\span\omit[{M}_{ab},{B}_{l}]=-(\delta_{a,l-1}-\delta_{b,l-1}+%&#10;\delta_{bl}-\delta_{al}){J}_{ab}\\&#10;\end{array}" text="Array[[closed-interval@(J _ (a * b), J _ (a * c)) = omega _ (a * b) * J _ (b * c), closed-interval@(J _ (a * b), J _ (b * c)) = -   <para xml:id="p9">
    <equation frefnum="(9)" labels="LABEL:CKsuCR" refnum="9" xml:id="S0.E9">
      <Math mode="display" tex="[{J}_{ab},{M}_{ab}]=-2{\omega}_{ab}\sum_{s=a+1}^{b}{B}_{s}\qquad\qquad[{B}_{k}%&#10;,{B}_{l}]=0" text="formulae@(closed-interval@(J _ (a * b), M _ (a * b)) = - 2 * omega _ (a * b) * ((sum _ (s = a + 1)) ^ b)@(B _ s), closed-interval@(B _ k, B _ l) = 0)" xml:id="S0.E9.m1">
        <XMath>
          <XMDual>
            <XMApp>
              <XMTok meaning="formulae"/>
              <XMRef idref="S0.E9.m1.1"/>
              <XMRef idref="S0.E9.m1.2"/>
            </XMApp>
            <XMWrap>
              <XMApp xml:id="S0.E9.m1.1">
                <XMTok meaning="equals" role="RELOP">=</XMTok>
                <XMDual>
                  <XMApp>
                    <XMTok meaning="closed-interval"/>
                    <XMRef idref="S0.E9.m1.1.1"/>
                    <XMRef idref="S0.E9.m1.1.2"/>
                  </XMApp>
                  <XMWrap>
                    <XMTok role="OPEN" stretchy="false">[</XMTok>
                    <XMApp xml:id="S0.E9.m1.1.1">
                      <XMTok role="SUBSCRIPTOP" scriptpos="post2"/>
                      <XMTok font="italic" role="UNKNOWN">J</XMTok>
                      <XMApp>

      <Math mode="display" tex="\langle U\&gt;a|U\&gt;b\rangle_{\omega}=\langle\&gt;a|\&gt;b\rangle_{\omega}\qquad\forall%&#10;\,\&gt;a,\&gt;b\in{{\mathbb{C}}}^{N+1}," text="formulae@((inner-product@(U * a, U * b)) _ omega = list@((inner-product@(a, b)) _ omega, for-all@(a)), b element-of C ^ (N + 1))" xml:id="S0.E13.m1">

          <XMDual>

  <para xml:id="p35">
    <equation frefnum="(33)" labels="LABEL:suBasicExtCoef" refnum="33" xml:id="S0.E33">
      <Math mode="display" tex="\begin{array}[]{ll}{\eta}_{ac}=-{\xi}({J}_{ab},{J}_{bc})&amp;\quad{\tau}_{ac}=-{%&#10;\xi}({J}_{ab},{M}_{bc})\\&#10;{\alpha}_{k}={\xi}({J}_{k-1\,k},{M}_{k-1\,k})&amp;\quad{\beta}_{kl}={\xi}({B}_{k},%&#10;{B}_{l})\end{array}" text="Array[[eta _ (a * c) = - xi * open-interval@(J _ (a * b), J _ (b * c)), tau _ (a * c) = - xi * open-interval@(J _ (a * b), M _ (b * c))], [alpha _ k = xi * open-interval@(J _ (k - 1 * k), M _ (k - 1 * k)), beta _ (k * l) = xi * open-interval@(B _ k, B _ l)]]" xml:id="S0.E33.m1">
        <XMath>
          <XMArray role="ARRAY" vattach="middle">
            <XMRow>
              <XMCell align="left">
                <XMApp>
                  <XMTok meaning="equals" role="RELOP">=</XMTok>
                  <XMApp>
                    <XMTok role="SUBSCRIPTOP" scriptpos="post7"/>
                    <XMTok font="italic" name="eta" role="UNKNOWN">η</XMTok>
                    <XMApp>
                      <XMTok meaning="times" role="MULOP">⁢</XMTok>
                      <XMTok font="italic" fontsize="70%" role="UNKNOWN">a</XMTok>
                      <XMTok font="italic" fontsize="70%" role="UNKNOWN">c</XMTok>
                    </XMApp>
                  </XMApp>
                  <XMApp>
                    <XMTok meaning="minus" role="ADDOP">-</XMTok>
                    <XMApp>
                      <XMTok meaning="times" role="MULOP">⁢</XMTok>
                      <XMTok font="italic" name="xi" role="UNKNOWN">ξ</XMTok>

      <Math mode="display" tex="\begin{array}[]{llll}{j}_{ab,de}&amp;\qquad{m}_{ab,de}&amp;\qquad{jm}_{ab,de}&amp;\qquad{%&#10;mj}_{ab,de}\cr{jb}_{ab,k}&amp;\qquad{mb}_{ab,k}&amp;\qquad{b}_{k,l}&amp;\qquad{jm}_{ab}\cr%&#10;{ji}_{ab}&amp;\qquad{mi}_{ab}&amp;\qquad{bi}_{l}&amp;\end{array}" text="Array[[j _ (list@(a * b, d * e)), m _ (list@(a * b, d * e)), j * m _ (list@(a * b, d * e)), m * j _ (list@(a * b, d * e))], [j * b _ (list@(a * b, k)), m * b _ (list@(a * b, k)), b _ (list@(k, l)), j * m _ (a * b)], [j * i _ (a * b), m * i _ (a * b), b * i _ l, ]]" xml:id="S0.E56.m1">

  <para xml:id="p68">
    <equation frefnum="(66)" labels="LABEL:CKsuExtB" refnum="66" xml:id="S0.E66">
      <Math mode="display" tex="\begin{array}[]{ll}[{J}_{ab},{B}_{a}]=-{M}_{ab}-{jb}_{ab,a}\Xi&amp;[{M}_{ab},{B}_{%&#10;a}]={J}_{ab}+{mb}_{ab,a}\cr[{J}_{ab},{B}_{a+1}]={M}_{ab}+{jb}_{ab,a+1}\Xi&amp;[{M}%&#10;_{ab},{B}_{a+1}]=-{J}_{ab}-{mb}_{ab,a+1}\Xi\quad b\geq a+2\cr[{J}_{a\,a+1},{B}%&#10;_{a+1}]=2{M}_{a\,a+1}+2{jb}_{a\,a+1,a+1}\Xi&amp;[{M}_{a\,a+1},{B}_{a+1}]=-2{J}_{a%&#10;\,a+1}-2{mb}_{a\,a+1,a+1}\Xi\cr[{J}_{ab},{B}_{b}]={M}_{ab}+{jb}_{ab,b}\Xi&amp;[{M}%&#10;_{ab},{B}_{b}]=-{J}_{ab}-{mb}_{ab,b}\Xi\quad b\geq a+2\cr[{J}_{ab},{B}_{b+1}]=%&#10;-{M}_{ab}-{jb}_{ab,b+1}\Xi&amp;[{M}_{ab},{B}_{b+1}]={J}_{ab}+{mb}_{ab,b+1}\Xi\cr[{%&#10;J}_{ab},{B}_{j}]={jb}_{ab,j}\Xi&amp;[{M}_{ab},{B}_{j}]={mb}_{ab,j}\Xi\end{array}" text="Array[[closed-interval@(J _ (a * b), B _ a) = - M _ (a * b) - j * b _ (list@(a * b, a)) * Xi, closed-interval@(M _ (a * b), B _ a) = J _ (a * b) + m * b _ (list@(a * b, a))], [closed-interval@(J _ (a * b), B _ (a + 1)) = M _ (a * b) + j * b _ (list@(a * b, a + 1)) * Xi, formulae@(closed-interval@(M _ (a * b), B _ (a + 1)) = - J _ (a * b) - m * b _ (list@(a * b, a + 1)) * Xi, b &gt;= a + 2)], [closed-interval@(J _ (a * a + 1), B _ (a + 1)) = 2 * M _ (a * a + 1) + 2 * j * b _ (list@(a * a + 1, a + 1)) * Xi, closed-interval@(M _ (a * a + 1), B _ (a + 1)) = - 2 * J _ (a * a + 1) - 2 * m * b _ (list@(a * a + 1, a + 1)) * Xi], [closed-interval@(J _ (a * b), B _ b) = M _ (a * b) + j * b _ (list@(a * b, b)) * Xi, formulae@(closed-interval@(M _ (a * b), B _ b) = - J _ (a * b) - m * b _ (list@(a * b, b)) * Xi, b &gt;= a + 2)], [closed-interval@(J _ (a * b), B _ (b + 1)) = - M _ (a * b) - j * b _ (list@(a * b, b + 1)) * Xi, closed-interval@(M _ (a * b), B _ (b + 1)) = J _ (a * b) + m * b _ (list@(a * b, b + 1)) * Xi], [closed-interval@(J _ (a * b), B _ j) = j * b _ (list@(a * b, j)) * Xi, closed-interval@(M _ (a * b), B _ j) = m * b _ (list@(a * b, j)) * Xi]]" xml:id="S0.E66.m1">

      <Math mode="display" tex="\begin{array}[]{lll}\{{J}_{ab},{M}_{bc},{B}_{c+1}\}:&amp;\quad{j}_{ab,bc}={\eta}_{%&#10;ac}&amp;\quad c&lt;N\cr\{{J}_{ab},{M}_{bN},{B}_{N}\}:&amp;\quad{j}_{ab,bN}={\eta}_{aN}&amp;%&#10;\quad b&lt;N-1\cr\{{J}_{a\,N-1},{M}_{N-1\,N},{B}_{a}\}:&amp;\quad{m}_{a\,N-1,N-1\,N}=%&#10;{\eta}_{aN}&amp;\quad a&gt;0\cr\{{J}_{0\,N-1},{M}_{N-1\,N},{B}_{1}\}:&amp;\quad{m}_{0\,N-%&#10;1,N-1\,N}={\eta}_{0N}&amp;\cr\{{M}_{ab},{J}_{bc},{B}_{c+1}\}:&amp;\quad{m}_{ab,bc}={%&#10;\eta}_{ac}&amp;\quad c&lt;N\cr\{{M}_{ab},{J}_{bN},{B}_{N}\}:&amp;\quad{m}_{ab,bN}={\eta}_%&#10;{aN}&amp;\quad b&lt;N-1\cr\{{M}_{aN-1},{J}_{N-1N},{B}_{a}\}:&amp;\quad{j}_{aN-1,N-1N}={%&#10;\eta}_{aN}&amp;\quad a&gt;0\cr\{{M}_{0N-1},{J}_{N-1N},{B}_{1}\}:&amp;\quad{j}_{0N-1,N-1N}%&#10;={\eta}_{0N}\end{array}" text="Array[[set@(J _ (a * b), M _ (b * c), B _ (c + 1)) colon absent, j _ (list@(a * b, b * c)) = eta _ (a * c), c less N], [set@(J _ (a * b), M _ (b * N), B _ N) colon absent, j _ (list@(a * b, b * N)) = eta _ (a * N), b less N - 1], [set@(J _ (a * N - 1), M _ (N - 1 * N), B _ a) colon absent, m _ (list@(a * N - 1, N - 1 * N)) = eta _ (a * N), a &gt; 0], [set@(J _ (0 * N - 1), M _ (N - 1 * N), B _ 1) colon absent, m _ (list@(0 * N - 1, N - 1 * N)) = eta _ (0 * N), ], [set@(M _ (a * b), J _ (b * c), B _ (c + 1)) colon absent, m _ (list@(a * b, b * c)) = eta _ (a * c), c less N], [set@(M _ (a * b), J _ (b * N), B _ N) colon absent, m _ (list@(a * b, b * N)) = eta _ (a * N), b less N - 1], [set@(M _ (a * N - 1), J _ (N - 1 * N), B _ a) colon absent, j _ (list@(a * N - 1, N - 1 * N)) = eta _ (a * N), a &gt; 0], [set@(M _ (0 * N - 1), J _ (N - 1 * N), B _ 1) colon absent, j _ (list@(0 * N - 1, N - 1 * N)) = eta _ (0 * N), ]]" xml:id="S0.E79.m1">

    <equation frefnum="(80)" labels="LABEL:ci" refnum="80" xml:id="S0.E80">
      <Math mode="display" tex="\begin{array}[]{lll}\{{J}_{ab},{J}_{bc},{B}_{c+1}\}:&amp;\quad{jm}_{ab,bc}={\tau}_%&#10;{ac}&amp;\quad c&lt;N\cr\{{J}_{ab},{J}_{bN},{B}_{N}\}:&amp;\quad{jm}_{ab,bN}={\tau}_{aN}&amp;%&#10;\quad b&lt;N-1\cr\{{J}_{a\,N-1},{J}_{N-1\,N},{B}_{a}\}:&amp;\quad{mj}_{a\,N-1,N-1\,N}%&#10;={\tau}_{aN}&amp;\quad a&gt;0\cr\{{J}_{0\,N-1},{J}_{N-1\,N},{B}_{1}\}:&amp;\quad{mj}_{0\,%&#10;N-1,N-1\,N}={\tau}_{0N}&amp;\cr\{{M}_{ab},{M}_{bc},{B}_{c+1}\}:&amp;\quad{mj}_{ab,bc}=%&#10;{\tau}_{ac}&amp;\quad c&lt;N\cr\{{M}_{ab},{M}_{bN},{B}_{N}\}:&amp;\quad{mj}_{ab,bN}={\tau%&#10;}_{aN}&amp;\quad b&lt;N-1\cr\{{M}_{aN-1},{M}_{N-1N},{B}_{a}\}:&amp;\quad{jm}_{aN-1,N-1N}=%&#10;{\tau}_{aN}&amp;\quad a&gt;0\cr\{{M}_{0N-1},{M}_{N-1N},{B}_{1}\}:&amp;\quad{jm}_{0N-1,N-1%&#10;N}={\tau}_{0N},\end{array}" text="Array[[set@(J _ (a * b), J _ (b * c), B _ (c + 1)) colon absent, j * m _ (list@(a * b, b * c)) = tau _ (a * c), c less N], [set@(J _ (a * b), J _ (b * N), B _ N) colon absent, j * m _ (list@(a * b, b * N)) = tau _ (a * N), b less N - 1], [set@(J _ (a * N - 1), J _ (N - 1 * N), B _ a) colon absent, m * j _ (list@(a * N - 1, N - 1 * N)) = tau _ (a * N), a &gt; 0], [set@(J _ (0 * N - 1), J _ (N - 1 * N), B _ 1) colon absent, m * j _ (list@(0 * N - 1, N - 1 * N)) = tau _ (0 * N), ], [set@(M _ (a * b), M _ (b * c), B _ (c + 1)) colon absent, m * j _ (list@(a * b, b * c)) = tau _ (a * c), c less N], [set@(M _ (a * b), M _ (b * N), B _ N) colon absent, m * j _ (list@(a * b, b * N)) = tau _ (a * N), b less N - 1], [set@(M _ (a * N - 1), M _ (N - 1 * N), B _ a) colon absent, j * m _ (list@(a * N - 1, N - 1 * N)) = tau _ (a * N), a &gt; 0], [set@(M _ (0 * N - 1), M _ (N - 1 * N), B _ 1) colon absent, j * m _ (list@(0 * N - 1, N - 1 * N)) = tau _ (0 * N), ]]" xml:id="S0.E80.m1">

    <equation frefnum="(82)" labels="LABEL:cj" refnum="82" xml:id="S0.E82">
      <Math mode="display" tex="\begin{array}[]{lll}\{{J}_{ab},{M}_{ac},{B}_{c+1}\}:&amp;\quad{j}_{ab,ac}={\omega}%&#10;_{ab}{\eta}_{bc}&amp;\quad c&lt;N\cr\{{J}_{ab},{M}_{aN},{B}_{N}\}:&amp;\quad{j}_{ab,aN}={%&#10;\omega}_{ab}{\eta}_{bN}&amp;\quad b&lt;N-1\cr\{{J}_{a\,N-1},{M}_{aN},{B}_{N-1}\}:&amp;%&#10;\quad{m}_{a\,N-1,aN}={\omega}_{aN-1}{\eta}_{N-1\,N}&amp;\quad a&lt;N-2\cr\{{M}_{ab},{%&#10;J}_{ac},{B}_{c+1}\}:&amp;\quad{m}_{ab,ac}={\omega}_{ab}{\eta}_{bc}&amp;\quad c&lt;N\cr\{{%&#10;M}_{ab},{J}_{aN},{B}_{N}\}:&amp;\quad{m}_{ab,aN}={\omega}_{ab}{\eta}_{bN}&amp;\quad b&lt;%&#10;N-1\cr\{{M}_{aN-1},{J}_{aN},{B}_{N-1}\}:&amp;\quad{j}_{aN-1,aN}={\omega}_{aN-1}{%&#10;\eta}_{N-1\,N}&amp;\quad a&lt;N-2\cr\omit\span\omit\span\omit\{{J}_{N-2\,N-1},{M}_{N-%&#10;2\,N},{B}_{N-1}\}:\cr\omit\span\omit\span\omit\qquad{j}_{N-2\,N-1,N-2\,N}+{%&#10;\omega}_{N-2\,N-1}{\eta}_{N-1\,N}-2{m}_{N-2\,N-1,N-2\,N}=0\cr\omit\span\omit%&#10;\span\omit\{{M}_{N-2\,N-1},{J}_{N-2\,N},{B}_{N-1}\}:\cr\omit\span\omit\span%&#10;\omit\qquad-2{j}_{N-2\,N-1,N-2\,N}+{\omega}_{N-2\,N-1}{\eta}_{N-1\,N}+{m}_{N-2%&#10;\,N-1,N-2\,N}=0\end{array}" text="Array[[set@(J _ (a * b), M _ (a * c), B _ (c + 1)) colon absent, j _ (list@(a * b, a * c)) = omega _ (a * b) * eta _ (b * c), c less N], [set@(J _ (a * b), M _ (a * N), B _ N) colon absent, j _ (list@(a * b, a * N)) = omega _ (a * b) * eta _ (b * N), b less N - 1], [set@(J _ (a * N - 1), M _ (a * N), B _ (N - 1)) colon absent, m _ (list@(a * N - 1, a * N)) = omega _ (a * N - 1) * eta _ (N - 1 * N), a less N - 2], [set@(M _ (a * b), J _ (a * c), B _ (c + 1)) colon absent, m _ (list@(a * b, a * c)) = omega _ (a * b) * eta _ (b * c), c less N], [set@(M _ (a * b), J _ (a * N), B _ N) colon absent, m _ (list@(a * b, a * N)) = omega _ (a * b) * eta _ (b * N), b less N - 1], [set@(M _ (a * N - 1), J _ (a * N), B _ (N - 1)) colon absent, j _ (list@(a * N - 1, a * N)) = omega _ (a * N - 1) * eta _ (N - 1 * N), a less N - 2], [set@(J _ (N - 2 * N - 1), M _ (N - 2 * N), B _ (N - 1)) colon absent], [(j _ (list@(N - 2 * N - 1, N - 2 * N)) + omega _ (N - 2 * N - 1) * eta _ (N - 1 * N)) - 2 * m _ (list@(N - 2 * N - 1, N - 2 * N)) = 0], [set@(M _ (N - 2 * N - 1), J _ (N - 2 * N), B _ (N - 1)) colon absent], [(- 2 * j _ (list@(N - 2 * N - 1, N - 2 * N))) + omega _ (N - 2 * N - 1) * eta _ (N - 1 * N) + m _ (list@(N - 2 * N - 1, N - 2 * N)) = 0]]" xml:id="S0.E82.m1">

                            <XMTok fontsize="70%" meaning="1" role="NUMBER">1</XMTok>

    </equation>
  </para>
  <para xml:id="p85">
    <equation frefnum="(83)" labels="LABEL:ck" refnum="83" xml:id="S0.E83">
      <Math mode="display" tex="\begin{array}[]{lll}\{{J}_{ab},{J}_{ac},{B}_{c+1}\}:&amp;\quad{jm}_{ab,ac}={\omega%&#10;}_{ab}{\tau}_{bc}&amp;\quad c&lt;N\cr\{{J}_{ab},{J}_{aN},{B}_{N}\}:&amp;\quad{jm}_{ab,aN}%&#10;={\omega}_{ab}{\tau}_{bN}&amp;\quad b&lt;N-1\cr\{{J}_{a\,N-1},{J}_{aN},{B}_{N-1}\}:&amp;%&#10;\quad{mj}_{a\,N-1,aN}={\omega}_{aN-1}{\tau}_{N-1\,N}&amp;\quad a&lt;N-2\cr\{{M}_{ab},%&#10;{M}_{ac},{B}_{c+1}\}:&amp;\quad{mj}_{ab,ac}={\omega}_{ab}{\tau}_{bc}&amp;\quad c&lt;N\cr%&#10;\{{M}_{ab},{M}_{aN},{B}_{N}\}:&amp;\quad{mj}_{ab,aN}={\omega}_{ab}{\tau}_{bN}&amp;%&#10;\quad b&lt;N-1\cr\{{M}_{aN-1},{M}_{aN},{B}_{N-1}\}:&amp;\quad{jm}_{aN-1,aN}={\omega}_%&#10;{aN-1}{\tau}_{N-1\,N}&amp;\quad a&lt;N-2\cr\omit\span\omit\span\omit\{{J}_{N-2\,N-1},%&#10;{J}_{N-2\,N},{B}_{N-1}\}:\cr\omit\span\omit\span\omit\qquad{jm}_{N-2\,N-1,N-2%&#10;\,N}+{\omega}_{N-2\,N-1}{\tau}_{N-1\,N}+2{mj}_{N-2\,N-1,N-2\,N}=0\cr\omit\span%&#10;\omit\span\omit\{{M}_{N-2\,N-1},{M}_{N-2\,N},{B}_{N-1}\}:\cr\omit\span\omit%&#10;\span\omit\qquad-2{jm}_{N-2\,N-1,N-2\,N}+{\omega}_{N-2\,N-1}{\tau}_{N-1\,N}-{%&#10;mj}_{N-2\,N-1,N-2\,N}=0\hfil.\end{array}" text="Array[[set@(J _ (a * b), J _ (a * c), B _ (c + 1)) colon absent, j * m _ (list@(a * b, a * c)) = omega _ (a * b) * tau _ (b * c), c less N], [set@(J _ (a * b), J _ (a * N), B _ N) colon absent, j * m _ (list@(a * b, a * N)) = omega _ (a * b) * tau _ (b * N), b less N - 1], [set@(J _ (a * N - 1), J _ (a * N), B _ (N - 1)) colon absent, m * j _ (list@(a * N - 1, a * N)) = omega _ (a * N - 1) * tau _ (N - 1 * N), a less N - 2], [set@(M _ (a * b), M _ (a * c), B _ (c + 1)) colon absent, m * j _ (list@(a * b, a * c)) = omega _ (a * b) * tau _ (b * c), c less N], [set@(M _ (a * b), M _ (a * N), B _ N) colon absent, m * j _ (list@(a * b, a * N)) = omega _ (a * b) * tau _ (b * N), b less N - 1], [set@(M _ (a * N - 1), M _ (a * N), B _ (N - 1)) colon absent, j * m _ (list@(a * N - 1, a * N)) = omega _ (a * N - 1) * tau _ (N - 1 * N), a less N - 2], [set@(J _ (N - 2 * N - 1), J _ (N - 2 * N), B _ (N - 1)) colon absent], [j * m _ (list@(N - 2 * N - 1, N - 2 * N)) + omega _ (N - 2 * N - 1) * tau _ (N - 1 * N) + 2 * m * j _ (list@(N - 2 * N - 1, N - 2 * N)) = 0], [set@(M _ (N - 2 * N - 1), M _ (N - 2 * N), B _ (N - 1)) colon absent], [((- 2 * j * m _ (list@(N - 2 * N - 1, N - 2 * N))) + omega _ (N - 2 * N - 1) * tau _ (N - 1 * N)) - m * j _ (list@(N - 2 * N - 1, N - 2 * N)) = 0]]" xml:id="S0.E83.m1">

      <Math mode="display" tex="\begin{array}[]{lll}\{{J}_{ac},{M}_{bc},{B}_{a}\}:&amp;\quad{m}_{ac,bc}={\omega}_{%&#10;bc}{\eta}_{ab}&amp;\quad a&gt;0\cr\{{J}_{0c},{M}_{bc},{B}_{1}\}:&amp;\quad{m}_{0c,bc}={%&#10;\omega}_{bc}{\eta}_{0b}&amp;\quad b&gt;1\cr\{{J}_{0c},{M}_{1c},{B}_{2}\}:&amp;\quad{j}_{0%&#10;c,1c}={\omega}_{1c}{\eta}_{01}&amp;\quad c&gt;2\cr\{{M}_{ac},{J}_{bc},{B}_{a}\}:&amp;%&#10;\quad{j}_{ac,bc}={\omega}_{bc}{\eta}_{ab}&amp;\quad a&gt;0\cr\{{M}_{0c},{J}_{bc},{B}_%&#10;{1}\}:&amp;\quad{j}_{0c,bc}={\omega}_{bc}{\eta}_{0b}&amp;\quad b&gt;1\cr\{{M}_{0c},{J}_{1%&#10;c},{B}_{2}\}:&amp;\quad{m}_{0c,1c}={\omega}_{1c}{\eta}_{01}&amp;\quad c&gt;2\cr\{{J}_{02}%&#10;,{M}_{12},{B}_{2}\}:&amp;\quad-2{j}_{02,12}+{\omega}_{12}{\eta}_{01}+{m}_{02,12}=0%&#10;\cr\{{M}_{02},{J}_{12},{B}_{2}\}:&amp;\quad 2{m}_{02,12}-{\omega}_{12}{\eta}_{01}-%&#10;{j}_{02,12}=0\end{array}" text="Array[[set@(J _ (a * c), M _ (b * c), B _ a) colon absent, m _ (list@(a * c, b * c)) = omega _ (b * c) * eta _ (a * b), a &gt; 0], [set@(J _ (0 * c), M _ (b * c), B _ 1) colon absent, m _ (list@(0 * c, b * c)) = omega _ (b * c) * eta _ (0 * b), b &gt; 1], [set@(J _ (0 * c), M _ (1 * c), B _ 2) colon absent, j _ (list@(0 * c, 1 * c)) = omega _ (1 * c) * eta _ 01, c &gt; 2], [set@(M _ (a * c), J _ (b * c), B _ a) colon absent, j _ (list@(a * c, b * c)) = omega _ (b * c) * eta _ (a * b), a &gt; 0], [set@(M _ (0 * c), J _ (b * c), B _ 1) colon absent, j _ (list@(0 * c, b * c)) = omega _ (b * c) * eta _ (0 * b), b &gt; 1], [set@(M _ (0 * c), J _ (1 * c), B _ 2) colon absent, m _ (list@(0 * c, 1 * c)) = omega _ (1 * c) * eta _ 01, c &gt; 2], [set@(J _ 02, M _ 12, B _ 2) colon absent, (- 2 * j _ (list@(02, 12))) + omega _ 12 * eta _ 01 + m _ (list@(02, 12)) = 0, ], [set@(M _ 02, J _ 12, B _ 2) colon absent, 2 * m _ (list@(02, 12)) - omega _ 12 * eta _ 01 - j _ (list@(02, 12)) = 0, ]]" xml:id="S0.E85.m1">

    <equation frefnum="(86)" labels="LABEL:cn" refnum="86" xml:id="S0.E86">
      <Math mode="display" tex="\begin{array}[]{lll}\{{J}_{ac},{J}_{bc},{B}_{a}\}:&amp;\quad{mj}_{ac,bc}={\omega}_%&#10;{bc}{\tau}_{ab}&amp;\quad a&gt;0\cr\{{J}_{0c},{J}_{bc},{B}_{1}\}:&amp;\quad{mj}_{0c,bc}={%&#10;\omega}_{bc}{\tau}_{0b}&amp;\quad b&gt;1\cr\{{J}_{0c},{J}_{1c},{B}_{2}\}:&amp;\quad{jm}_{%&#10;0c,1c}={\omega}_{1c}{\tau}_{01}&amp;\quad c&gt;2\cr\{{M}_{ac},{M}_{bc},{B}_{a}\}:&amp;%&#10;\quad{jm}_{ac,bc}={\omega}_{bc}{\tau}_{ab}&amp;\quad a&gt;0\cr\{{M}_{0c},{M}_{bc},{B}%&#10;_{1}\}:&amp;\quad{jm}_{0c,bc}={\omega}_{bc}{\tau}_{0b}&amp;\quad b&gt;1\cr\{{M}_{0c},{M}_%&#10;{1c},{B}_{2}\}:&amp;\quad{mj}_{0c,1c}={\omega}_{1c}{\tau}_{01}&amp;\quad c&gt;2\cr\{{J}_{%&#10;02},{J}_{12},{B}_{2}\}:&amp;\quad 2{jm}_{02,12}-{\omega}_{12}{\tau}_{01}-{mj}_{02,%&#10;12}=0\cr\{{M}_{02},{M}_{12},{B}_{2}\}:&amp;\quad-{jm}_{02,12}-{\omega}_{12}{\tau}_%&#10;{01}+2{mj}_{02,12}=0.\end{array}" text="Array[[set@(J _ (a * c), J _ (b * c), B _ a) colon absent, m * j _ (list@(a * c, b * c)) = omega _ (b * c) * tau _ (a * b), a &gt; 0], [set@(J _ (0 * c), J _ (b * c), B _ 1) colon absent, m * j _ (list@(0 * c, b * c)) = omega _ (b * c) * tau _ (0 * b), b &gt; 1], [set@(J _ (0 * c), J _ (1 * c), B _ 2) colon absent, j * m _ (list@(0 * c, 1 * c)) = omega _ (1 * c) * tau _ 01, c &gt; 2], [set@(M _ (a * c), M _ (b * c), B _ a) colon absent, j * m _ (list@(a * c, b * c)) = omega _ (b * c) * tau _ (a * b), a &gt; 0], [set@(M _ (0 * c), M _ (b * c), B _ 1) colon absent, j * m _ (list@(0 * c, b * c)) = omega _ (b * c) * tau _ (0 * b), b &gt; 1], [set@(M _ (0 * c), M _ (1 * c), B _ 2) colon absent, m * j _ (list@(0 * c, 1 * c)) = omega _ (1 * c) * tau _ 01, c &gt; 2], [set@(J _ 02, J _ 12, B _ 2) colon absent, 2 * j * m _ (list@(02, 12)) - omega _ 12 * tau _ 01 - m * j _ (list@(02, 12)) = 0, ], [set@(M _ 02, M _ 12, B _ 2) colon absent, (- j * m _ (list@(02, 12)) - omega _ 12 * tau _ 01) + 2 * m * j _ (list@(02, 12)) = 0, ]]" xml:id="S0.E86.m1">
